title: Fabbri gets tiebreaker in 3rd as Blues beat Oilers, McDavid (Yahoo Sports)
text: Posts: 54,145 Fabbri gets tiebreaker in 3rd as Blues beat Oilers, McDavid (Yahoo Sports) ST. LOUIS (AP) -- Rookie Robby Fabbri scored the tiebreaking goal midway through the third period to help the St. Louis Blues beat Edmonton 3-1 Thursday night, spoiling Oilers rookie Connor McDavid's NHL debut.
